#http://www.epicurious.com/recipes/food/views/Caesar-Salad-with-Sourdough-Croutons-361234
IN	4 anchovy fillets, finely chopped
IN	2 garlic cloves, minced
IN	1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice
IN	1 tablespoon red wine vinegar
IN	1 tablespoon Dijon mustard
IN	11/2 teaspoons Worcestershire sauce
IN	1/3 cup extra-virgin olive oil
IN	3/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese, divided
IN	2 large hearts of romaine lettuce, torn into bite-size pieces (about 12 cups)
IN	1 1/2 cups sourdough croutons
IN	Chopped fresh Italian parsley
PR	Whisk first 6 ingredients in small bowl. Gradually whisk in oil, then 1/2 cup cheese.
PR	Toss lettuce, croutons, 1/4 cup cheese, and dressing in bowl. Sprinkle with parsley and season to taste with pepper.
